  "detailed_description": "<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/WishlistGiff.gif?t=1719318592\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/eac2a3859acf380707fc63283909964a.poster.avif?t=1719318592\" width=800 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/eac2a3859acf380707fc63283909964a.webm?t=1719318592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/eac2a3859acf380707fc63283909964a.mp4?t=1719318592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Burglar Inc. is an immersive strategy and simulation game that turns you into a master thief. You must plan your heists, develop your skills, and use the latest technology to rob wealthy homes. You can also team up with 3 friends and pull off heists together.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/6943d550eece4b54a9b134442ec32abf.poster.avif?t=1719318592\" width=800 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/6943d550eece4b54a9b134442ec32abf.webm?t=1719318592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/6943d550eece4b54a9b134442ec32abf.mp4?t=1719318592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Stealth and Planning: You must plan each heist in detail, analyze the security systems of homes and businesses, and find ways to get in and out without being detected.<br><br><strong>Customize Your Burglar</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/ce613066ccddcba4caec8ea57df2d1bf.poster.avif?t=1719318592\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/ce613066ccddcba4caec8ea57df2d1bf.webm?t=1719318592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/ce613066ccddcba4caec8ea57df2d1bf.mp4?t=1719318592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Check Stock Market</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/8327c43dafa8c468fce021f409a3af4f.poster.avif?t=1719318592\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/8327c43dafa8c468fce021f409a3af4f.webm?t=1719318592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/8327c43dafa8c468fce021f409a3af4f.mp4?t=1719318592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Check stock market before selling your stolen goods. Stock market updates daily!<br><br><strong>Beware of the security systems!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/e5d9aa7e69c46d6125620725fac063ad.poster.avif?t=1719318592\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/e5d9aa7e69c46d6125620725fac063ad.webm?t=1719318592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/e5d9aa7e69c46d6125620725fac063ad.mp4?t=1719318592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Cameras: Make sure that you have Camera Detector<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/aa685351af338f417c6ff45cc09b8b68.poster.avif?t=1719318592\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/aa685351af338f417c6ff45cc09b8b68.webm?t=1719318592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/aa685351af338f417c6ff45cc09b8b68.mp4?t=1719318592\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Lasers: You can see them with a spray.<br><br><strong>You can hack CCTV for your advantage.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/64b82f9ea05fa338dfc4ae156b28ceed.poster.avif?t=1719318592\" width=570 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/64b82f9ea05fa338dfc4ae156b28ceed.webm?t=1719318592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Get better: Improve your skills in lockpicking, disabling alarm systems, and moving silently to take on more challenging heists.<br><br>Technology: Use advanced burglary tools and equipment to make your job easier.<br><br>Co-op: Team up with friends and pull off heists together. Each of you can have different tools and must work in a coordinated way to complete the heist successfully.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/d43d98217e36df832b034de09bf34be3.poster.avif?t=1719318592\" width=570 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798810/extras/d43d98217e36df832b034de09bf34be3.webm?t=1719318592\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>In-Game Voice Chat: Communicate with your teammates in real-time and coordinate your plans. However! Be careful, if you speak loudly, unexpected events may happen.",
